<br>
The elemental...just root the elemental, fear the chick, nuke the piss out of the elemental, loot and zone.<br>
<br>
Gimblox...take yer time going to his spawn so you got plenty of mana (come in the back door past the merchant gobs).  Then just kill the 2 by the pit and park yer butt on Gim's spawn. <p><Br><img src="http://www.student.nvcc.vccs.edu/home/tlazaroff/CR.jpg" border="0">
